// src/messages.js
export const messages = [
  {
    id: 1,
    sender: 'Alice',

    message: 'Hey! How are you doing?',

  },
  {

    sender: 'You',
    receiver: 'Alice',

    sender: 'Alice',
    receiver: 'You',
    profilePicture: 'https://via.placeholder.com/50',

    receiver: 'Alice',

    timestamp: '2025-01-21T10:42:00',

  {
    id: 7,
    sender: 'Charlie',
    receiver: 'You',
    profilePicture: 'https://via.placeholder.com/50',
    message: 'Don’t forget about the meeting later.',
    timestamp: '2025-01-21T10:45:00',
  },
  {
    id: 8,
    sender: 'You',
    receiver: 'Charlie',
    profilePicture: 'https://via.placeholder.com/50',
    message: 'Thanks for the reminder! See you there.',
    timestamp: '2025-01-21T10:50:00',
  },
];
